      • isPreloadAllDIEs

        public boolean isPreloadAllDIEs()
        Option to cause the DWARF parser to load all DWARF records into memory, instead of processing one compile unit at a time. Needed to handle binaries created by some toolchains. The import pre-check will warn the user if this needs to be turned on.
        Returns:
        boolean flag

      • setPreloadAllDIEs

        Parameters:
        b - boolean flag to set
